The dealer spins the roulette wheel in one direction while releasing the ball in the opposite direction.

Outcome:
The winning number is displayed on the screen in which the ball lands after the wheel comes to a stop.
Players who placed bets on the winning number, color, or category win according to the game's payout rules.

