Straight/Single Bet:
 Betting on a single number (35 x 1).

Row Bet:
 Betting on horizontal row of numbers (2 x 1).

Column Bet:
 Betting on a vertical column of numbers (2 x 1).

Dozen Bet:
 Betting on one of three groups of numbers (1-12, 13-24, 25-36)  (2 x 1).

